high_descs: Move over to the counter between the microwave and the sink.
Pick up the butter knife on the counter.
Turn around and go to the table behind. you.
Cut the loaf of bread on the back of the table into slices.
Turn back around and go to the sink.
Place the knife inside the sink.
Turn back around to the table, where the bread is.
Remove the end slice of bread, nearest to you.
Turn around and go to the microwave.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, heat it up, then remove it from the microwave.
Turn to your right and go to the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the slice of bread on the counter top, near the edge.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in the sink and a warm slice of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the counter between the sink and microwave.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go to the wall, hang a left and go to the table with the bread on it.
Cut the bread that is on the table into slices.
Turn to the left, go to the sink that is ahead on the left.
Put the knife in the sink.
Turn to the left, go to the wall, hang a left and go to the bread on the table.
Pick up a slice of bread from the table.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn around to face the microwave.
Put the bread inside the microwave and turn it on to cook, remove the bread when it is done cooking.
Turn around, go to the counter that is to the right of the sink.
Put the bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked bread on the counter.

high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and cross the room to face the end of the table.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn around to face the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Turn around to face the bread on the table.
Pick up the slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around to face the microwave.
Heat the bread slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn right and walk forward and turn left to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the bread slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a bread slice and place it on the counter to the right of the stove.
